title: Goal Getters
description: "You get what you work for and not what you wish for" has been Jessi and Stew's mantra for the last couple of years and they decided to dedicate this entire season to help listeners understand what it means to be a Goal Getter and how you can achieve the career and life of your dreams! And that means mastering the practice of turning thoughts into ideas and turning those ideas into actions. Jessi and Stew are sharing their secrets and the steps they take to S.M.A.R.T goal-setting.
